Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.06,0:00:12.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玉液觥籌明日香
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.85,0:00:21.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流民夜話訴肝腸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.81,0:00:30.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孤魂只求歌一闕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.18,0:00:40.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閒人不知輕袖揚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.77,0:02:42.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.49,0:03:00.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做了個夢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.91,0:03:02.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎樣的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:04.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.16,0:03:06.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,記不起來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.60,0:03:11.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明知道這個夢已經做過很多次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.54,0:03:16.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是一醒來就記不起到底夢見了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.44,0:03:26.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等你身體再好一點 我就把所有真相告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.78,0:03:29.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一點一點地慢慢告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.80,0:03:33.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果一口氣全都告訴你的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.23,0:03:38.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定會覺得我瘋了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.41,0:03:41.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還痛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.83,0:03:42.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.85,0:03:44.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是覺得不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.06,0:03:46.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就會習慣的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.72,0:03:50.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在唯一可以告訴你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.58,0:04:00.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我們的愛比世界上任何一對男女都要深
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.80,0:04:13.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.78,0:04:15.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空襲警報
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.91,0:04:18.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在日本正在和美國交戰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.12,0:04:20.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美國？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.03,0:04:36.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.77,0:04:38.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往這邊過來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.28,0:04:39.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.43,0:04:40.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追兵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.67,0:04:42.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們正在被追殺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.41,0:04:49.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.21,0:05:10.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.41,0:05:28.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你回到東京了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.48,0:05:30.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑蜜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.81,0:06:45.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.25,0:06:49.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救…命…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.49,0:07:00.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.25,0:07:02.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還好你沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.33,0:07:05.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.71,0:07:06.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.26,0:07:15.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 從前…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.61,0:07:18.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從前也發生過這樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.76,0:07:28.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在黑暗中與她一起逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.09,0:07:32.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.61,0:07:36.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比在那次更早 以及在更遙遠的從前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.63,0:07:39.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的事也一次一次地重演
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.44,0:07:54.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些我不都是知道的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.57,0:08:21.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.89,0:08:33.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真美
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.34,0:08:35.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.15,0:08:37.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.96,0:08:43.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類再也無法污染大氣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.41,0:08:48.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生命也再不會因此滅絕了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.22,0:08:54.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.47,0:11:19.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.77,0:11:22.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.61,0:11:23.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萊依
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.66,0:11:25.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天那個叫歌留多的傢伙的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.83,0:11:30.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你睡著了所以對你稍微調查了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.93,0:11:33.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天的事還記得沒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.30,0:11:36.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赤帝軍和你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.44,0:11:47.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃了這麼大虧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.77,0:11:49.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些傢伙不會罷休的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.39,0:11:52.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們會遭到報復
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.65,0:11:54.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許有很多人會死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.85,0:11:58.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是應該負下責任啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.70,0:11:59.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,責任？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.48,0:12:06.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如來埴輪跟我們一起干
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.23,0:12:14.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.76,0:12:16.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.56,0:12:20.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那兒通電了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.46,0:12:22.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好危險 差點你就沒命了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.23,0:12:27.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦 來坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.25,0:12:30.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微聊會兒天也好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.76,0:12:33.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去拿喝的 你等下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.90,0:12:51.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在找什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.12,0:12:52.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.53,0:12:57.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要說「從冬眠中甦醒的蛇」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.48,0:13:01.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.97,0:13:07.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得我曾經有過這樣的二人生活
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.76,0:13:09.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.50,0:13:11.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也可能是夢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.70,0:13:13.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不確定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.86,0:13:17.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可真怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.21,0:13:19.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.24,0:13:20.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快涼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.38,0:13:25.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者說你更希望來點人血
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.28,0:13:34.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你昨天根本就不是個正常人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.28,0:13:36.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直是個怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.99,0:13:39.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.41,0:13:41.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還有事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.31,0:13:43.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是黑蜜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.01,0:13:47.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在找的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.15,0:13:49.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.83,0:13:54.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們能為你提供關於黑蜜的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.21,0:13:57.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過前提是你要加入我們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.31,0:13:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.47,0:14:00.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.50,0:14:14.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是改主意了可以去那家畫有蛇頭的肉店
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.32,0:14:18.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想知道的東西只能在那兒找到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.99,0:14:35.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,報告我看了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.60,0:14:38.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過難以置信啊 萊依
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.52,0:14:42.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因為你沒看見酒船的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.69,0:14:44.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個叫九郎的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.34,0:14:46.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,力氣大得嚇人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.89,0:14:49.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真假難辨 不可靠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.29,0:14:52.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算真的是他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.22,0:14:53.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是他？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.38,0:14:55.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼意思 居座魚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.17,0:14:57.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他要是來了帶到我房間來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.35,0:14:59.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解散
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.27,0:15:29.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在找什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.08,0:15:30.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.22,0:15:37.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從冬眠中甦醒的蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.28,0:15:40.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.75,0:15:57.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你果然來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.61,0:15:58.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.64,0:16:04.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久遠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.33,0:16:06.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找居座魚有事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.69,0:16:10.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又從哪兒找來的垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.43,0:16:12.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.20,0:16:13.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.21,0:16:14.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居座魚等了很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.06,0:16:17.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.79,0:16:19.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把刀交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.97,0:16:23.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九郎就不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.86,0:16:25.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居座魚已經知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.84,0:16:27.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別難為他了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.56,0:16:28.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九郎 你進去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.09,0:16:30.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那個房間
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.18,0:16:39.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放開
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.28,0:16:45.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是九郎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.90,0:16:50.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居座魚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.46,0:16:53.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這兒的負責人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.47,0:16:56.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.71,0:16:59.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是保存御稜威必要的溫度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.75,0:17:00.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御稜威？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.89,0:17:03.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不能落到別人手上的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.35,0:17:08.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們要我幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.97,0:17:12.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來驅鬼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.34,0:17:19.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赤帝軍熱衷於探求生命的奧秘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.95,0:17:23.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了實驗劫持人民
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.59,0:17:25.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眾多的生命無辜地犧牲了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.74,0:17:26.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,實驗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.78,0:17:28.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.98,0:17:31.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都是因為血
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.52,0:17:33.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.58,0:17:35.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們需要戰友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.05,0:17:37.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果願意跟我們一起並肩作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.71,0:17:39.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就可以讓你見她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.03,0:17:41.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.67,0:18:00.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密地下室？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.12,0:18:04.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居座魚看來是想帶他去那兒看看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.00,0:18:07.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連我們都不讓看的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.17,0:18:10.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九郎到底是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.49,0:18:51.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,20年前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.00,0:18:53.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赤帝軍在這兒挾持了黑蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.03,0:18:58.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,試圖用她的血來製造魔人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.96,0:19:04.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我們必須從他們手上奪回黑蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.48,0:19:06.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我們最大的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.35,0:19:08.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.33,0:19:11.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想救黑蜜的話就跟我們一起戰鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.28,0:19:17.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.55,0:19:22.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帶走黑蜜的是赤帝軍?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.08,0:19:24.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少騙我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.89,0:19:26.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.22,0:19:27.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別裝蒜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.09,0:19:31.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帶走黑蜜的人不就是你們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.20,0:19:33.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.42,0:19:36.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從我身邊帶走黑蜜的人根本不是赤帝軍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.41,0:19:39.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人 是你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.37,0:19:51.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來真的是你 九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.51,0:19:57.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 我們秘藏了黑蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.48,0:20:00.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的血就等同於武器
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.98,0:20:03.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,決不能交給敵…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.53,0:20:08.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能再相信你們說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.48,0:20:10.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先讓我見黑蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.76,0:20:12.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他的事之後再說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.30,0:20:15.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好像不太明白自己的處境
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.23,0:20:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吸血鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.88,0:20:23.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是拒絕的話就只能讓你死在這兒了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.85,0:20:32.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩個都給我住手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.97,0:20:41.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你聽著 九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.98,0:20:45.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能見黑蜜由沙仁輪來決定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.13,0:20:48.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根據你接下來的表現
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.74,0:20:50.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把劍收起來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.05,0:21:02.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌留多
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.57,0:21:04.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都聽見了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.03,0:21:06.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被發現啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.29,0:21:10.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天帶九郎去沙仁輪那兒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.08,0:21:11.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.09,0:21:13.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過居座魚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.52,0:21:15.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的沒問題？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.50,0:21:18.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帶陌生人去見她

